## Photosynthesis Flowchart (Mermaid)

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Sunlight H2O] --> B(Light-Dependent Reactions LDR);
    B --> C{Thylakoid Membrane};
    C --> D(O2 Release);
    C --> E[ATP + NADPH];
    E --> F{Stroma / Calvin Cycle};
    G[CO2] --> F;
    F --> H[G3P / Glucose Synthesis];
    F --> I[Regeneration of ADP + NADP+];
    I --> B;

    style A fill:#ffcc00,stroke:#333
    style D fill:#90ee90,stroke:#333
    style H fill:#add8e6,stroke:#333
    style B fill:#f9f,stroke:#333
    style F fill:#ccc,stroke:#333
```

**Key Labels:**
*   **A:** Initial Inputs
*   **B:** LDR (Energy Capture)
*   **C:** Location of LDR (Thylakoid)
*   **D:** Byproduct (Oxygen)
*   **E:** Energy Carriers (Outputs of LDR, Inputs to LIR)
*   **F:** LIR (Carbon Fixation)
*   **G:** Essential Input ($CO_2$)
*   **H:** Final Product (Sugar)
*   **I:** Energy Carriers recycled back to LDR
